## Validation Commands

```text
show system interface
get system interface
execute ping-options source 10.10.10.2
execute ping 10.10.10.1
```

## Rollback Hint

Remove only VLAN interfaces created by this plan: VLANs 30, 40, 50, and 60. Do not delete `hlvl`, `mgt`, or any VLAN 20 objects as part of this FortiGate plan.
